  "texts": [
    "Optimization of Object Detection AlgorithmsAs research on object detection algorithms advances, the challenges and difficulties that need to be addressed have been increasing, especially in complex traffic scenarios.",
    "In such scenarios, a single scene can involve multiple objects.",
    "It is, therefore, necessary to extract the features of each object individually.",
    "When objects occlude each other, detection accuracy tends to decrease.",
    "Moreover, due to the complexity of traffic scenes, images obtained from these scenes often have lower quality."
  ],
